Transparency & accountability:

content:
2/ Why is this important‚ùì

Anyone can issue a scam token or NFT project. For example, scam tokens can be spun out of thin air, listed on a Dex, and marketed to investors. Given how common anonymous founders are in crypto, bringing scammers to accountability is always a challenge
